OL,6,GWhen a massive news story breaks at
OL,7,Gthe weekend it can prove a challenge
OL,8,Gfor the main TV bulletins.
OL,10,FEven in an age of 24-hour news, the
OL,11,Fimportance to many people of the main
OL,12,FBBC One and ITV 1 bulletins must not
OL,13,Fbe forgotten.
OL,15,FSaturday's mutiny by the Russian
OL,16,Fmercenary force Wagner was exactly
OL,17,Fthat scenario.
OL,3,CHow BBC One and ITV 1 react to big
OL,4,Cbreaking news at weekends
