OL,6,FThe reports from Russia were
OL,7,Fconfused. For a period, it looked
OL,8,Flike there was a real threat of a
OL,9,Fnuclear power descending into chaos
OL,10,For even civil war.
OL,12,FIn an age of 24-hour news, staffing
OL,13,Fthese stories is not an issue. Many
OL,14,Fcorrespondents are, essentially,
OL,15,Frequired to be available when
OL,16,Frequired.
OL,18,FThe BBC News Channel and Sky News
OL,19,Foffered special programming and
OL,20,Frolling coverage but what of the two
OL,21,Fmain general channels?
OL,3,CHow BBC One and ITV 1 react to big
OL,4,Cbreaking news at weekends
