OL,6,FITV 1 bulletins were business as
OL,7,Fusual ` visually and duration-wise.
OL,9,FBut over at W1A, the public service
OL,10,Fbroadcaster's flagship channel has
OL,11,Fdifferent responsibilities and
OL,12,Fdilemmas. Covering a major story at a
OL,13,Ftime of week when the focus is on
OL,14,Frelaxation and entertainment.
OL,16,FBBC One definitely benefits from the
OL,17,Ffact that Breakfast is now
OL,18,Festablished as part of the weekend
OL,19,Fschedule. Of the other three
OL,20,Fbulletins on Saturday, two were
OL,21,Fextended slightly.
