OL,6,FMy own view is that BBC One should
OL,7,Fhave been prepared to allow more
OL,8,Fsignificant extensions to the
OL,9,Fdurations.
OL,11,FUnfolding events in Russia were
OL,12,Fcovered as comprehensively as they
OL,13,Fwould have been during the week `
OL,14,Fespecially on the late bulletin which
OL,15,Fwas, by fortunate coincidence of
OL,16,Ftiming, able to adopt the persona of
OL,17,Fthe BBC News at Ten complete with Huw
OL,18,FEdwards.
OL,3,CHow BBC One and ITV 1 react to big
OL,4,Cbreaking news at weekends
