OL,6,FHuw came in specially to present and
OL,7,Fthe programme was presented from its
OL,8,Fnormal set ` not the newsroom studio
OL,9,Fnormally still used on Saturdays.
OL,11,FBut the duration was insufficient to
OL,12,Fallow any other stories to be covered
OL,13,Fand there was no Saturday sports
OL,14,Fround-up.
OL,16,FThis was a lost opportunity. When a
OL,17,Fmajor story happens, it's important
OL,18,Fnot to lose sight of other things
OL,19,Feven if stories are bound to be
OL,20,Fsqueezed out.
