OL,6,FThere's a lesson here for those in
OL,7,Fcharge of BBC One ` remember that the
OL,8,Fnews is one of the channel's biggest
OL,9,Fassets. I'm sure BBC News would have
OL,10,Fno trouble making the necessary
OL,11,Frepresentations.
OL,13,FThe fact weekday branding was adopted
OL,14,Fand that Huw came in to present
OL,15,Freminded me of a very different time.
OL,17,FIn the mid-1980s the weekend news
OL,18,Fservice seemed to suffer from a
OL,19,Fdegree of benign neglect.
