OL,6,FIn October 1986, President Reagan met
OL,7,FPresident Gorbachev for a weekend
OL,8,Fsummit on Iceland.
OL,10,FJohn Humphrys was brought in to
OL,11,Fpresent the weekend bulletins and
OL,12,Fslight modifications were made to the
OL,13,Fnormal weekend presentation.
OL,15,FA few months later, came the tragedy
OL,16,Fof the Zeebrugge ferry disaster.
OL,18,FA special edition of Breakfast Time `
OL,19,Fby then a news-based programme `
OL,20,Freplaced some of Saturday Superstore.
