OL,6,FAt lunchtime, a full edition of the
OL,7,FOne O'Clock News ` presented by
OL,8,FMartyn Lewis and with its normal
OL,9,Fweekday branding ` was shown during
OL,10,FGrandstand.
OL,12,FThe evening bulletins were an unusual
OL,13,Fhybrid.
OL,15,FThey still used the normal weekend
OL,16,Fsets and titles. But Martyn stayed on
OL,17,Fto present and the One's graphics
OL,18,Fpackage was used ` together with the
OL,19,Fastons normally used by the daytime
OL,20,Fsummaries.
