OL,6,FA year later, the weekend
OL,7,Finconsistency was addressed when the
OL,8,FNine o'Clock News was relaunched. The
OL,9,Fweekend bulletins used the Nine's
OL,10,Fgraphics and the main bulletins were
OL,11,Falways presented by one of the Nine's
OL,12,Fpresenters.
OL,14,FThis helped to ensure that when big
OL,15,Fnews broke at the weekend, the effort
OL,16,Fwas on making sure the newsgathering
OL,17,Foperstion was up to speed ` nobody
OL,18,Fneeded to worry about whether the
OL,19,Funderlying standard or authority of
OL,20,Fweekend presentation was adequate.
OL,22,FSo are there lessons from yesterday?
