OL,6,FI'm increasingly sure there is a case
OL,7,Ffor fixing the time of the main
OL,8,FSaturday bulletin at 10pm ` a
OL,9,Fsolution can be found just as one was
OL,10,Ffound for Sundays in 2000.
OL,12,FThe bulletin could still be moved on
OL,13,Fexceptional occasions including the
OL,14,FEurovision Song Contest, the Last
OL,15,FNight of the Proms and the Strictly
OL,16,Ffinal.
OL,18,FThe programme should move
OL,19,F"downstairs" to the main weekday set
